quran[13{c,v,t}:
27,64,aur kon hai jo Khalq ki ibtida karta aur phir is ka iada karta hai? aur kon tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta hai? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein hissa daar ) hai? kaho ke lao apni Daleel agar tum sachey ho
27,65,"inn se kaho, Allah ke siwa asmano aur zameen mein koi ghaib ka ilm nahi rakhta, aur woh nahi jantay ke kab woh uthaye jayen ge"
27,66,"balkay akhirat ka to ilm hi inn logon se gum ho gaya hai, balkay yeh is ki taraf se shak mein hain, balkay yeh uss se andhay hain"
27,67,"yeh munkareen kehte hain"" kya jab hum aur hamaray baap dada matti ho chuke hon ge to hamein waqai qabron se nikala jaye ga ?"
27,68,"yeh khabrain hum ko bhi bohat di gayi hain aur pehlay hamaray aaba ajdaad ko bhi di jati rahi hain, magar yeh bas afsaanay hi afsaanay hain jo aglay waqton se suntay chalay aa rahay hain """
27,69,kaho zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekho ke mujrimon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai
27,70,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn ke haal par ranj nah karo aur nah inn ki chalon par dil tang ho"
27,71,"woh kehte hain ke"" yeh dhamki kab poori ho gi agar tum sachey ho? """
27,72,kaho kya ajab ke jis azaab ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay ho is ka aik hissa tumahray qareeb hi aa laga ho
27,73,haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab to logon par bara fazl frmane wala hai magar aksar log shukar nahi karte
27,74,bulaa shuba tera rab khob jaanta hai jo kuch un ke seenay apne andar chupaye hue hain aur jo kuch woh zahir karte hain
27,75,aasman o zameen ki koi posheeda cheez aisi nahi hai jo aik wazeh kitaab mein likhi hui mojood nah ho
27,76,yeh waqea hai ke yeh quran bani Israel ko aksar unn baton ki haqeeqat batata hai jin mein woh ikhtilaaf rakhtay hain
